achievements.title: HPV Vaccination Awareness Campaign
achievements.description:
I actively participated in an online HPV vaccination awareness campaign representing SYNCH society on TWITTER.Through consistent posting and engagement with, our team under the supervision of DHO Islamabad, successfully made it trending topic.
This initiative strengthened my passion for public health advocacy.

achievements.title: Global Fatty Liver Disease Day
achievements.description: I actively attended the Global Fatty Liver Disease Day, 12th June, 2025 webinar conducted by Medicos Aid Society to actively contribute to awareness of hepatic patients in Holly Family Hospital, Rawalpindi regarding liver diseases like Hemochromatosis, Wilson's disease, Hepatocellular Carcinoma etc as they present global health burden.

reflections.title: Old Age home Visit
reflections.content: This visit to Old Age home was not just a service but an experience to revive my purpose  which is not just about treating but also about understanding human emotions and ethical practice of empathy.

reflections.title: Cirrhosis Case Observation and Counselling
reflections.content: My Uncle, 45 years old,presented with  a case of Cirrhosis with complications of portal hypertension. His family struggled with the idea of long-term progressive illness. This was the moment where I could connect the science with empathy. My contribution, though small, helped the family better understand the disease process.Under the guidance of my teachers, I was able to counsel him for this disease and encourage him for life-style modifications with nutritional intake of high protein diet and vitamins.

reflections.title: Presentation on Mediastinum
reflections.content: Preparing  for this presentation on Mediastinum, its subdivisions,contents and clinical significance, required me to study in depth and simplify complex anatomical details. I realised that teaching is one of the best ways of learning. It highlighted the importance of collaborative learning and sharing knowledge with relevance.
